Q1/- What is JDBC, Write a note on JDBC driver software

ans=> 
     JDBC is a technology that is establish the connection of 
     any type of java application to any type of DATA BASE s/w;
     in a standard manner;
     
     JDBC technology is given by SON-MicroSystem;
     
     JDBC driver s/w is the implementation of the jdbc specification
     which will act as a translator s/w to communicate our java application 
     with the data base s/w 
     
     